1期會有冒險樂園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無理由青衣咁多小朋友都無一間冒險樂園㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：鐘意夾公仔而已</blockquote><br />\n長發老麥對面咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實說，我好少行到去長發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果可以搬去長衣城1、2期就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f129d3a6febe8fa13c643d9cf86d84e2fc3f737","tid":498023,"uid":74002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d63f15f9cf877f0fbabf5537b264f34b3e4081","tid":498023,"uid":63150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽講有魚尚<br />\n係咪會好過爭鮮？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/uoshow.hk/posts/1346816835447853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fuoshow.hk%2Fposts%2F1346816835447853&d=ZWeSRS2AzZMtAPOpxiHhOaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=03e850bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/uoshow.hk/posts/1346816835447853</a><br />\n<br />\n似係<br />\n<br />\n未食過，不過我覺得邊一間都會好過爭鮮㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n天橋個層麻<br />\n你行過就會見到，佢個鋪頭一早已經裝修好，個時連商場地下牆身都未整好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8b07978fc48aa32812020e0f66126ff4193fcf","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真，除咗本身住青衣同住東涌嘅人，邊鬼個會突登嚟青衣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405b4146844209963820d499d8ac36796c23227f","tid":498023,"uid":63150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新開咪比盡兩星期，咩都走哂啦D人<br />\n記唔記得90年代新開青衣城幾多人"},{"pid":"169c933f3d9aaa0448ab127db89ccbd4ae4387a7","tid":498023,"uid":54744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"係咪一期會整一田/aeon??<br />\n我老母聽d保安呀伯講話好似會整一田<br />\n不過我諗都係估"},{"pid":"b5f0b3a8278d40e29936e6480e33ea48edd47830","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新開咪比盡兩星期，咩都走哂啦D人<br />\n記唔記得90年代新開青衣城幾多人</blockquote><br />\n我都係近年先搬嚟青衣住<br />\n<br />\n我未搬嚟青衣之前真係從來都未曾去過青衣城<br />\n<br />\n以前成日以為青衣好似個荒島咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6b022c4f30b30f5f746979d5de5dc0d029ca36","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪一期會整一田/aeon??<br />\n我老母聽d保安呀伯講話好似會整一田<br />\n不過我諗都係估</blockquote><br />\n其實青衣城駛唔駛咁多超市<br />\n<br />\n本身有Taste, 宜家馬莎又有食品賣"},{"pid":"9183fc7b38fb1ec23ec486290002e42fcbcdc28a","tid":498023,"uid":30454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:55:47.000Z","msg":"Logon呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520b6ead04c8cbcfc81ada1726bc97a69ee89670","tid":498023,"uid":2008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇返個list，分分鐘遲啲1期仲好行過2期<br />\n<br />\n最好啲金舖/首飾舖搬埋過去仲更加好<br />\n<br />\n希望遲啲1期會有冒險樂園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無理由青衣咁多小朋友都無一間冒險樂園㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：鐘意夾公仔而已</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長發舊戲院個位會變冒險樂園 話會有大型迷宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果邊唔係AEON 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAEON已執柒, 果個位死位開乜都執"},{"pid":"345897d25e3e7ef3baa9ec85ab40083ff049a76f","tid":498023,"uid":63150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇返個list，分分鐘遲啲1期仲好行過2期<br />\n<br />\n最好啲金舖/首飾舖搬埋過去仲更加好<br />\n<br />\n希望遲啲1期會有冒險樂園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無理由青衣咁多小朋友都無一間冒險樂園㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：鐘意夾公仔而已</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長發舊戲院個位會變冒險樂園 話會有大型迷宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果邊唔係AEON 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAEON已執柒, 果個位死位開乜都執</blockquote><br />\n佢將美心放去個度已經算好，起馬真係有人會行去個度角位<br />\n以前仲係長發舊戲院時，去到零食鋪個位已經停步"},{"pid":"15b304ae7551ecbefa646585d36aa3b02de7d025","tid":498023,"uid":63150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新開咪比盡兩星期，咩都走哂啦D人<br />\n記唔記得90年代新開青衣城幾多人</blockquote><br />\n我都係近年先搬嚟青衣住<br />\n<br />\n我未搬嚟青衣之前真係從來都未曾去過青衣城<br />\n<br />\n以前成日以為青衣好似個荒島咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真實青衣真係一個荒島<br />\n已經講緊最旺既青衣城呢帶<br />\n我想像唔到幾廿個屋苑住左唔知幾多人，但可以零糖水鋪<br />\n又無娛樂場所"},{"pid":"358f980a5bc85a1c09f0b760e4f367a902771a5a","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"其實青衣城搞食咪算<br />\n<br />\n都無人買野既"},{"pid":"81d45377513e7c96d18907dea4acbca490af00c3","tid":498023,"uid":1327,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新開咪比盡兩星期，咩都走哂啦D人<br />\n記唔記得90年代新開青衣城幾多人</blockquote><br />\n我都係近年先搬嚟青衣住<br />\n<br />\n我未搬嚟青衣之前真係從來都未曾去過青衣城<br />\n<br />\n以前成日以為青衣好似個荒島咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真實青衣真係一個荒島<br />\n已經講緊最旺既青衣城呢帶<br />\n我想像唔到幾廿個屋苑住左唔知幾多人，但可以零糖水鋪<br />\n又無娛樂場所</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左起係商場入面 我寧願佢冇<br />\n似荃灣既話樓下嘈撚到仆街又污糟<br />\n壓逼感又大 咁岩青衣冇哂呢d 野 <br />\n又冇d 紅 van 片黎片去 周圍行 又多公園<br />\n真係住得好舒服"},{"pid":"b4500fa749307782721a3f3de007803116dc9007","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Logon呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLogon 對我真係可有可無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣啲嘢咁鬼貴"},{"pid":"df9f0679502169fc37e539113ba6511d49ce2366","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇返個list，分分鐘遲啲1期仲好行過2期<br />\n<br />\n最好啲金舖/首飾舖搬埋過去仲更加好<br />\n<br />\n希望遲啲1期會有冒險樂園啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無理由青衣咁多小朋友都無一間冒險樂園㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：鐘意夾公仔而已</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長發舊戲院個位會變冒險樂園 話會有大型迷宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果邊唔係AEON 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAEON已執柒, 果個位死位開乜都執</blockquote><br />\n咁死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70077c1cb459c2677306ddcbfa5ad62940850cfc","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n真實青衣真係一個荒島<br />\n已經講緊最旺既青衣城呢帶<br />\n我想像唔到幾廿個屋苑住左唔知幾多人，但可以零糖水鋪<br />\n又無娛樂場所</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假假地都有一間許留山嘅<br />\n<br />\n娛樂場所唔駛諗啦<br />\n<br />\n換轉你係Neway 老闆，你會唔會諗住響青衣開分店吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 厭＄多咩"},{"pid":"0fd07f58659e4063513a614f6424d576f3c71fa3","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T22:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實青衣城搞食咪算<br />\n<br />\n都無人買野既</blockquote><br />\n絕對贊成啦<br />\n<br />\n搞個類似大食代Food Court 無咁嬲"},{"pid":"8d7d2ab2263306f034fd7ca369878cd941bd6a36","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實青衣城搞食咪算<br />\n<br />\n都無人買野既</blockquote><br />\n絕對贊成啦<br />\n<br />\n搞個類似大食代Food Court 無咁嬲</blockquote><br />\n呢區既人根本無消費力"},{"pid":"371202ee86ecbb65e13254f404b1268ccbb52a72","tid":498023,"uid":16147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會變到新都會咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都係倒模商場一個 但就個個湧哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新開咪比盡兩星期，咩都走哂啦D人<br />\n記唔記得90年代新開青衣城幾多人</blockquote><br />\n我都係近年先搬嚟青衣住<br />\n<br />\n我未搬嚟青衣之前真係從來都未曾去過青衣城<br />\n<br />\n以前成日以為青衣好似個荒島咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真實青衣真係一個荒島<br />\n已經講緊最旺既青衣城呢帶<br />\n我想像唔到幾廿個屋苑住左唔知幾多人，但可以零糖水鋪<br />\n又無娛樂場所</blockquote><br />\