normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n青衣乜柒都冇得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荃灣葵芳又好多野玩咩"},{"pid":"b34d46fb281d13fd1b62691de9cfe655574930f5","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實青衣城搞食咪算<br />\n<br />\n都無人買野既</blockquote><br />\n絕對贊成啦<br />\n<br />\n搞個類似大食代Food Court 無咁嬲</blockquote><br />\n呢區既人根本無消費力</blockquote><br />\n如果認真要買嘢消費，啲人情願再搭多一個站去東涌，果邊又多outlet，真正可以大手掃貨<br />\n<br />\n所以青衣嘅商場客源真係只係針對返青衣居民<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞咁多奇奇怪怪舖頭啦"},{"pid":"f1cf46a0af74556fcf94380b9a903f760d7513a7","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n翠怡商場有間甜品鋪都幾好食</blockquote><br />\n果間每次去親都好多人<br />\n<br />\n仲未有機會試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dfa2dffe95930c1523f9fc38f8dcf9345e8a71","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n翠怡商場有間甜品鋪都幾好食</blockquote><br />\n你咁講太興果邊都有間好好野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋兩個應該講緊同一間"},{"pid":"8a0c4684379e41bb2b7457886ad08e6a80fadd3d","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真青衣人去玩多數都去荃灣葵芳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n青衣乜柒都冇得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荃灣葵芳又好多野玩咩</blockquote><br />\n荃灣愉景新城、中染新城、南豐+新之城呢一帶都多嘢玩啦<br />\n<br />\n近排Metroplaza 裝修完後都多嘢行咗<br />\n<br />\n呢兩邊都係兒童天地"},{"pid":"bbfb154e3dc43a03188eff0b8ce74ef7eb1cdaf2","tid":498023,"uid":138999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"我間嘉禾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92012353000e2d2d911ebe384be90f336c2332f8","tid":4980