/>\n<br />\n搞個類似大食代Food Court 無咁嬲</blockquote><br />\n呢區既人根本無消費力</blockquote><br />\n如果認真要買嘢消費，啲人情願再搭多一個站去東涌，果邊又多outlet，真正可以大手掃貨<br />\n<br />\n所以青衣嘅商場客源真係只係針對返青衣居民<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞咁多奇奇怪怪舖頭啦</blockquote><br />\n除左青衣人 山卡啦其實有三間酒店 <br />\n不時都有人係青衣站出閘 再上去<br />\n所以都叫有少少旅客生意 <br />\n不過個幾間酒店真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果到出葵芳仲快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e225c7965f84465299b7e5c5223df547126c19e","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實青衣城搞食咪算<br />\n<br />\n都無人買野既</blockquote><br />\n絕對贊成啦<br />\n<br />\n搞個類似大食代Food Court 無咁嬲</blockquote><br />\n呢區既人根本無消費力</blockquote><br />\n如果認真要買嘢消費，啲人情願再搭多一個站去東涌，果邊又多outlet，真正可以大手掃貨<br />\n<br />\n所以青衣嘅商場客源真係只係針對返青衣居民<br />\n<br />\n唔好搞咁多奇奇怪怪舖頭啦</blockquote><br />\n其實青衣都有自由行<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地買野會出旺角"},{"pid":"7b344ae106bf9ea401b582b9092270601afa0943","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n翠怡商場有間甜品鋪都幾好食</blockquote><br />\n你咁講太興果邊都有間好好野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋兩個應該講緊同一間</blockquote><br />\n火焰雪山好正"},{"pid":"b4c658d154bda647db13fef1955c418d084fed02","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講真青衣人去玩多數都去荃灣葵芳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n青衣乜柒都冇得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n荃灣葵芳又好多野玩咩</blockquote><br />\n荃灣愉景新城、中染新城、南豐+新之城呢一帶都多嘢玩啦<br />\n<br />\n近排Metroplaza 裝修完後都多嘢行咗<br />\n<br />\n呢兩邊都係兒童天地</blockquote><br />\n請問呢批商場有咩玩？"},{"pid":"4f425465716081aee3f36bdb400b62e7b758357f","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪一期會整一田/aeon??<br />\n我老母聽d保安呀伯講話好似會整一田<br />\n不過我諗都係估</blockquote><br />\n其實青衣城駛唔駛咁多超市<br />\n<br />\n本身有Taste, 宜家馬莎又有食品賣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarks &amp; Spenser 之前係1樓賣食品</blockquote><br />\n好貴"},{"pid":"be52f71d5370762cc5e3e7d60efeb35433859a4b","tid":498023,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"仲未見青衣城入面有宣傳"},{"pid":"295ff4190990e4ae3af0f254a1484dfebbbb661e","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n請問呢批商場有咩玩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你嘅&ldquo;玩&rdquo;係指咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於有小朋友嘅我，我覺得真係好多嘢玩<br />\n<br />\n有玩具反斗城、有Namco Wonder Park、有遊樂設施等<br />\n<br />\n如果你話Neway, Bowling 果啲大人玩嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我承認真係無囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976701ae870f47cb1a078ec8617a9a418871bc3f","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未見青衣城入面有宣傳</blockquote><br />\n聽日第一日就直踩入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7dcbf0183e97a672a191da370884a5c6fa740d","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n除左青衣人 山卡啦其實有三間酒店 <br />\n不時都有人係青衣站出閘 再上去<br />\n所以都叫有少少旅客生意 <br />\n不過個幾間酒店真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n限死啲旅客只去葵涌廣場、metroplaza 同青衣城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fe38816ed1c918863794aeb0ee234ff5a4fe94","tid":498023,"uid":138106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"青衣南其實唔錯，幾舒服。出葵芳又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08067bc9194467dfa2e50781b2c2752d5e1fc586","tid":498023,"uid":2819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:02:46.000Z","msg":"天日開張"},{"pid":"e4b77c3c3c86719b4c135fff6d7bbe932cf96893","tid":498023,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:12:56.000Z","msg":"青衣得海皮個邊好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf40bc9efc34337a21fba607289426384b139b","tid":498023,"uid":139814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"青衣除左住之外真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩食所有嘢最近都要去荃灣葵芳"},{"pid":"4a5bcc94bb848ce38e4a864aa88745c5245e5e59","tid":498023,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青衣除左住之外真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩食所有嘢最近都要去荃灣葵芳</blockquote><br />\n我十年無去過呢兩區"},{"pid":"50f883facdbb49c25a9ba6c5e6068ca0610b4995","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/205706_0e25212a529f0e427e58ffb85cf4f331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F205706_0e25212a529f0e427e58ffb85cf4f331.jpg&h=65d69f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備就緒"},{"pid":"6b7f85898bb2526ff729f5b12a958fc0e48cba72","tid":498023,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:58:44.000Z","msg":